e head` before browser verification. The tracked source tree is otherwise clean; only harness-owned `.yolopilot` run files remain uncommitted.", "type": "agent_message"}, "type": "item.completed"}, "task_display_context": {"event_number": 570, "prompt_index": 54, "prompt_name": "53 \u2014 Outline Drill-Down From Beats to Chapters or Scenes", "prompt_total": 100}, "timestap": "2026-04-02T03:12:30-07:00"}
